snippet.title: Mere Husband Ki Biwi | Official Trailer | Arjun, Rakul, Bhumi | Mudassar | 21 Feb
snippet.description:
Get ready for the Biggest Siyappa this season, kyuki yeh love triangle nahi, full circle hai! 🔄
#MereHusbandKiBiwi Trailer Out Now!

#MereHusbandKiBiwi In Cinemas on 21st February, 2025

Mere Husband Ki Biwi -  A hilarious and heartwarming modern-day romance set in Delhi, where love, fate, and unexpected twists put one man in a chaotic dilemma. Caught between a rekindled spark with Antara and an unexpected twist with Prabhleen, Ankur’s life takes a hilariously unpredictable turn. Starring Arjun Kapoor, Rakulpreet Singh, Bhumi Pednekar, to name a few.

#MereHusbandKiBiwiOnFebruary21

Finance Minister Nirmala Sitharaman presented her 8th Union Budget to the Parliament on 1st February 2025. The Budget covered different proposals for the Indian Economy.
In this video, Abhi and Niyu have covered important points from the Budget proposals, explained how the new tax slabs and rebate works, and explain how the Union Budget works. 

Here are some of the important proposals mentioned in the Budget:
* Nuclear Energy Mission
* Support to Footwear Industry (both leather and non leather)
* Makhana Board for Bihar
* Support to Make in India Toys
* Shipbuilding Financial Assistance Policy
* Policy to procure pulses directly from farmers on contract farming basis
* Modified UDAN scheme
* National Repository of Indian Knowledge books
* Bharat TRADENET
* High Level Committee for non financial sector regulatory reforms

Sources: 
Economic Survey: https://www.indiabudget.gov.in/economicsurvey/
Budget: https://www.indiabudget.gov.in/

Finance Minister Nirmala Sitharaman presented her 8th Union Budget to the Parliament on 1st February 2025. The Budget covered different proposals for the Indian Economy.
In this video, Abhi and Niyu have covered important points from the Budget proposals, explained how the new tax slabs and rebate works, and explain how the Union Budget works. 

Here are some of the important proposals mentioned in the Budget:
* Nuclear Energy Mission
* Support to Footwear Industry (both leather and non leather)
* Makhana Board for Bihar
* Support to Make in India Toys
* Shipbuilding Financial Assistance Policy
* Policy to procure pulses directly from farmers on contract farming basis
* Modified UDAN scheme
* National Repository of Indian Knowledge books
* Bharat TRADENET
* High Level Committee for non financial sector regulatory reforms

snippet.title: Saraswati Vandana | Shreya Ghoshal
snippet.description:
Shreya Ghoshal embarks on a new musical journey with devotion at its heart, beginning with a Saraswati Vandana—a sacred ode to the goddess of wisdom, music, and the arts. This newly composed hymn beautifully captures the essence of Ma Saraswati’s grace, symbolising the purity of mind, intellectual and spiritual enlightenment and creativity. Enriched by the ethereal voice of Shreya Ghoshal, whose pristine vocal texture brings unmatched beauty, the melody flows like a sacred offering, uplifting the soul and invoking the goddess’s blessings. Her vocals seamlessly weave into the poignant notes of Sarod and the lush choral arrangements. This musical offering is an invitation to immerse in the profound peace and inspiration that Ma Saraswati personifies.

Singer - Shreya Ghoshal

Guitars – Abhishek Dasgupta
Programming - Abhishek Mestry

Music Arranger - Kinjal Chatterjee

Lyrics:
Om Saraswatyai Namah
(Salutations to Goddess Saraswati)

Om

Ya Kundendu Tusharharadhavala
(She who is as white as the jasmine flower, the moon, and a garland of snow)

Ya Kundendu Tusharaharadhavala
(She who is as white as the jasmine flower, the moon, and a garland of snow)

Ya Shubhra Vastravrita
(She who is adorned with pure white garments)

Ya Veena Varadanda ManditaKara
(She whose hands are adorned with the divine veena)

Ya Shweta Padmasana
(She who is seated on a white lotus throne)

Ya Brahmachyuta Shankara Prabhritibhir Devai Sada Pujita
(She who is always worshiped by Brahma, Vishnu, and Shiva)


Sa Maam Patu Saraswati Bhagavati Nishesh Jaadyapaha
(May that goddess Saraswati, who removes all ignorance, protect me.)

Om Saraswatyai Namo Namah
(Salutations and reverence to Goddess Saraswati)

Om

Saraswati Namastubhyam Varade Kaamarupini
(Salutations to you, Goddess Saraswati, who grants boons and fulfiller of wishes)

Saraswati Namastubhyam Varade Kaamarupini
(Salutations to you, Goddess Saraswati, who grants boons and fulfiller of wishes)

Vidyarambham Karishyami Siddhir Bhavatu Me Sada
(I am beginning my pursuit of knowledge; may I always attain success)

(Salutations to you, Goddess Saraswati, who grants boons and fulfiller of wishes)

snippet.title: Jaane Tu | Chhaava | Vicky Kaushal, Rashmika Mandanna | A. R. Rahman, Arijit Singh, Irshad Kamil
snippet.description:
Jaane Tu, Jaanu Main…

For the powerful love behind the powerful warrior, ‘Jaane Tu’ is a romantic ballad for the ages. Combining the three maestros of music – A. R. Rahman, Arijit Singh and Irshad Kamil, it features Vicky Kaushal and Rashmika Mandanna in the video.  From the highly anticipated movie ‘Chhaava’, this is the first song release from the movie.

#JaaneTu #ARRahman #ArijitSingh #IrshadKamil #VickyKaushal #RashmikaMandanna #AkshayeKhanna #Chhaava 

🎵Stream Now: https://smi.lnk.to/JaaneTu

Jaane tu jaanun main
Meri jaan tu hi Thi tu hi hai
Ye saansein kya saansein
Inka aana jaana yun hi hai
Meri Jaan tu Hai
Tu thi haan tu hai
Jaane tu jaanun main

Tere honthon honthon pe vaade mere
Tere honthon honthon pe baatein meri
Chain jaisa tera khayal
Dheere dheere aaye

Mere honthon honthon pe vaade tere
Mere honthon honthon pe baatein teri
Lafz mere lena sanbhaal
In mein tere saaye

Dekho kya kya bataayein
Baagi hawayein
Dheeme suron mein gaayein... ho

Jaane tu jaanun main
Meri jaan tu hi thi tu hi hai
Ye saansein kya saansein
Inka aana jaana yun hi hai
Meri Jaan tu Hai
Tu thi haan tu hai
Jaane tu jaanun main

Kya dard hai
Kya chot hai
Tere khayal mein hun
Mujhko na hosh hai

Tu saath hai mere
Lahu mein hai khushi
Maine na tootna
Main vaada hun tumhara

snippet.title: Celebrating the Year of the Snake! 🐍 Clash of Clans New Season
snippet.description:
Legendary snakes of the Clash lands are ushering in an age of celebration! Get in on the Lunar festivities, unleash mystical Snake Heroes, and start training for some ludicrously Lunar challenges and Events ahead! Visit the sky-high home of the ancient elemental snakes with the Year of the Snake Legendary Scenery and transform your Village into a serene sanctuary where the celebrations never end!

Follow us on our Socials!
Twitter ► https://twitter.com/ClashofClans/
Instagram ► https://www.instagram.com/clashofclans 
Facebook ► https://www.facebook.com/ClashofClans 
TikTok ► https://www.tiktok.com/@clashofclans

Attack. Defend. Strategize. Download for free for mobile devices. supr.cl/PlayClashOfClans

From rage-­filled Barbarians with glorious mustaches to pyromaniac wizards, raise your own army and lead your clan to victory! Build your village to fend off raiders, battle against millions of players worldwide, and forge a powerful clan with others to destroy enemy clans.
PLEASE NOTE! Clash of Clans is free to download and play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money 

Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash of Clans.
A network connection is also required.

FEATURES
- Build your village into an unbeatable fortress 
- Raise your own army of Barbarians, Archers, Hog Riders, Wizards, Dragons and other mighty fighters
- Battle with players worldwide and take their Trophies
- Join together with other players to form the ultimate Clan
- Fight against rival Clans in epic Clan Wars 
- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

Chief, are you having problems? Visit https://help.supercellsupport.com/clash-of-clans/en/

Privacy Policy:
https://supercell.com/en/privacy-policy/

Terms of Service:
https://supercell.com/en/terms-of-service/

snippet.title: Dilli Ki Winters | The Paayal Jain
snippet.description:
Hey Guys , 
Hope you enjoy this winter video . We love you so much .

Click on Link To Buy Himalaya Serum - https://amzn.to/3EaXbc2

This video shows different behaviours of Indians during winters . Dilli Ki Winters is extreme .  This is a very comic and relatable video. When the temperature is falling and the heaters , hot water bags , heating pads , sweaters , sweatshirts , hoodies , coats , jackets , scarfs mufflers , gloves , thermals , socks , monkey caps , boots , comes to beat the cold especially if it's delhi winters . College exams during winters , School Board Exams with hot coffee or tea travelling by metro bikes in thand , shopping from sarojini market for latest winter fashion , planning winter trip to hills with friends to see snow , cause snowfall , bonfire with friends is the best time . indian moms covering kids in multiple layers of warm clothes to avoid cold and flue , Feeding winter green leafy vegetables , hara saag and  enjoying thand me gajar ka halwa , lazy winters in bed watching shows Tv serials anupama or christmas movies with hot chocolate , chai , heater , blanket perfect cosy environment .  Buying school winter uniform for kids , Mothers and their millions of excuses when it comes to exercising or changing life in sardiyan that sardi bht pad rhi he and alot more . All these winter problems that we all indians in winters face .

This video is filled with such memories and situations we all have been in. 
Relish and Relive your Memories.. You will love this .
Do share it with your friends and family  .. Comment down your Fav Part,

snippet.title: Snehan & Kannika Blessed with Twins! 👶👶 After 4 Years of Struggle | Snehan Emotional ❤️
snippet.description:
We are overjoyed to share this incredible blessing with all of you! 💖 Snehan and Kannika have been blessed with not one, but two little miracles—a baby boy and a baby girl! 🎊👶👶 In this special family vlog, we take you through the emotional journey of welcoming our twins into the world. From the first moments in the hospital to bringing them home, this is a celebration of love, faith, and family.

Thank you to everyone for your prayers, love, and support throughout this journey. We can't wait to share more precious moments with you all as our family grows! ❤️

Don’t forget to LIKE, COMMENT, and SUBSCRIBE for more updates on our beautiful journey as parents to these little blessings! 💕#snehan #kannika #snehanbaby #kannikasnehan #snehanchildren #biggbosssnehan #lyricistsnehan #NewsTamilGlitz #TamilNewsGlitz #newstamil24x7

snippet.title: Filmymoji || Middle Class Madhu || Mandala Deeksha || Final Episode || MCM
snippet.description:
Filmymoji Middle Class Madhu  Mandala Deeksha Final Episode MCM

The much-awaited climax of the Deeksha series on the FilmyMoji channel is here! In this gripping final episode, Madhu and his friends, along with Sarada Subbarao, embark on an intense spiritual journey—the Ayyappa Deeksha—culminating in a pilgrimage to the sacred Sabarimala Temple.

Plot Summary:

As the journey begins, the group faces multiple physical and emotional hurdles. They endure the rigorous 41-day Deeksha, following strict rules of celibacy, vegetarianism, and discipline. Throughout the journey, humor and camaraderie shine, especially with the presence of 1A Master, who adds his signature comic relief to the otherwise spiritual and serious narrative.

Upon reaching Sabarimala, they experience the challenge of climbing the sacred 18 steps (Pathinettu Padi), which symbolize the ultimate test of devotion. The emotional and spiritual highs of the journey are depicted beautifully, with divine moments that leave a lasting impact on the viewers.

Meanwhile, Ganesh, a key character in the story, faces an unexpected twist. Will he be able to complete his Deeksha successfully? Will the group have a fulfilling pilgrimage? The episode ties up all loose ends with a mix of devotion, comedy, and life lessons.

Why You Should Watch:

Spiritual Significance: A heartfelt depiction of Ayyappa Deeksha and the power of devotion.

Comedy & Emotions: The perfect blend of humor and sentiment, making it a wholesome watch.

Friendship & Brotherhood: A strong message about togetherness and faith.

Climax with a Twist: A surprising turn that keeps you engaged till the very end.


Don’t miss out on this emotional and uplifting finale! Swamiye Saranam Ayyappa!

 കൃപാസനത്തിൽ മാസത്തിലെ എല്ലാ ദിവസങ്ങളിലും  പുതുതായി ഉടമ്പടി എടുക്കാനും ഉടമ്പടി എടുത്തവർക്ക് പുതുക്കുവാനും  സാക്ഷ്യം പറയാനുമുള്ള  സൗകര്യം ഉണ്ടായിരിക്കുന്നതാണ്( ഉടമ്പടി സമയം: 6am-2pm 
സാക്ഷ്യ സമയം: 10am - 5pm)

 മുമ്പിൽ സമയമില്ലാത്ത എല്ലാ വിഷയങ്ങളും   പ്രാർത്ഥന വിഷയങ്ങൾ പങ്കുവയ്ക്കുന്നതിനായി  ബഹുമാനപ്പെട്ട ജോസഫച്ചൻ എടുക്കുന്നതാണ്.അതിനായി നിങ്ങൾ തീർത്ഥാടക ഉടമ്പടി എടുത്തതിനുശേഷം ഈ നമ്പറിൽ (9447285400) നിങ്ങൾ വരുന്ന ദിവസം അച്ചൻ ഉണ്ടോ ഇല്ലയോ എന്ന് ഉറപ്പുവരുത്തേണ്ടതാണ്.

 ദിവസവും രാവിലെ  7.30 നും വൈകിട്ട് 6:30 നും കൃപാസനത്തിൽ ദിവ്യബലി ഉണ്ടായിരിക്കുന്നതാണ്.  

കൃപാസനം പത്രം നിലവിൽ 17 ഭാഷകളിൽ ലഭ്യമാണ്!

Vallavanukku Pullum Aayudham  is a 2014 Indian Tamil-language action comedy film directed by Srinath and released by Studio Green on 9 May 2014. A remake of S. S. Composer: Anuv Jain, Shinda Kahlon, AP Dhillon
Lyrics: Anuv Jain, Shinda Kahlon, AP Dhillon, Reeka Jain

AFSOS (Lyrics)

A 1

Haan 
Teri yaadan yaadan 
Teri yaadan le ke betha 
Kai raatan raatan

Par aaj
Ena raatan picho
Meinu sab sach nazar ae aunda
Kivein akhan akhan?

B 1

Jo guroor si 
Oh fizool si 
Meinu aaj pata laga 
Ki kasoor si 

Mere dil de noor 
Main si mash-hoor 
Tenu karta dur 
Oh, bekasoor!

Kinj gairan nu 
Main apna mann 
Mileya mere apne nu 
Gair ban

Eh taan zaroor 
Dil karta choor
Tera

C 1 

Te haan
Main duniya vekhi 
Tere dil nu vekh na paya 
Main jhalla jhalla 

Karda si
Wadeya nawan di
Gallan gallan

Hun ethe
Marda janda 
Main kalla kalla

A 2

Hun kyun 
Afsos hoya?
Hun ki fayeda?
Milna ni
Je chahaan chahaan

Main hun
Ghadiya de hath te
Kivein modha 
Rukh samay da 
Te rahaan rahaan?

D 

Chand pal do pal 
Teri sunda battan je 

Tere nal hi 
Sab katda rattan je 

Tere hanju dekhda 
Vich barsattan je

Kitte karda teh 
Eh dil di vattan je 

B 2

Kaisi shaam si
Tere naam si 
Jo padheya na main
Ki pegham si?

Main hairan si
Naadan si
Kis gallon meri jaan
Pareshan si?

Tenu hasde vekh ke
Baar baar
Tenu puchi na main kadey tere
Dil di saar

Tera intezar, 
Meri samjho baar 
Kidda katey ne tu din metho 
Haar haar?

C 2

Haan
Jo pyaar si tera
Thoda vi samajh na paya 
Main jhalla jhalla 

Haan
Eh dil pachtave 
Tere bin hun reh na pave 
Eh kalla kalla

A 3

Hun kyun 
Afsos hoya?
Hun ki fayeda?
Milna ni
Je chahaan chahaan

Main hun
Ghadiya de hath te

Sunn Mera Dil Digitally Presented by LUX - Happilac Paints and Ujooba Beauty Cream

7th Sky Entertainment’s highly anticipated mega signature project, Sunn Mere Dil, is the most awaited drama serial. The mega drama boasts a star-studded cast led by Wahaj Ali and Maya Ali. Written by the renowned Khalil Ur Rehman Qamar and directed by the acclaimed Haseeb Hasan, Sunn Mere Dil promises to be a one-of-a-kind drama.

Sunn Mere Dil is a tale in which love finds a new meaning, where one person’s devotion quietly flourishes, often unnoticed. Their heart beats for someone who may never truly understand the depth of their feelings. Yet, in their silent sacrifices, they realize that true love is not about
possession but about selflessness.

Every unspoken gesture and unseen act of kindness brings them fulfillment, as they put their beloved’s happiness above their own, showing that love is not just about being together, it’s about redefining happiness, even at the expense of their contentment.

BALU SM 



ఊరంత సుట్టాలే నీ పెళ్ళికి పాట❤️‍🔥Full Song త్వరలో మీ ముందుకు వస్తుంది మొత్తం పాట ఇంక బాగుంటది 
ఈసారి🔥ఊరుఊరంతా ప్రతిపెల్లిలో వినపడుతుంది మీ అందరి Support కావాలి 🥹🙏


ఊరంత సుట్టాలే నీ పెళ్ళికి పాట Lyrics :-

పల్లవి :- 

మనసిచ్చిన అమ్మాయినే మనవాడలేనప్పుడు...
ప్రేమించిన అమ్మాయితోని జీవించలేనప్పుడు 

నా ప్రాణాలు ఎందుకమ్మా ......నీ పక్కన నేనే లేనప్పుడు 
నేను బతికుండుదెందుకమ్మా....నా బతుకంత నీతోని కానప్పుడు 

ఊరంత సుట్టాలె నీ పెండ్లికి 
వందేళ్ల కన్నీళ్లు నా కండ్లకి
బాధే లేదాయే నీ గుండెకి 
సావే మందాయె నాబాధకి —2

Episode 4308: Nakli Venukutti
--------------------------------------------------------
Nattu Kaka pretends to be Venukutti while Bagha takes on the role of a driver to carry out Jethalal's plan. Will they be able to pull it off?

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2024 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #16yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: SNAIL FRY | NATHAI VARUVAL | Snail Recipe Cooking and Eating in Village | Healthy Village Recipes
snippet.description:
Discover the art of traditional Snail Fry (Nathai Varuval) cooking in the heart of the village! 🐌✨ This unique recipe combines fresh, locally sourced snails with a blend of aromatic spices, creating a mouthwatering dish that’s as healthy as it is flavorful.

Watch as we prepare this delicacy from scratch, using simple yet time-tested techniques over a firewood stove. Every step showcases the charm of village cooking, from cleaning the snails to frying them to perfection.

What’s in the Recipe:

Fresh snails straight from nature
A medley of traditional spices
Gingelly oil and hand-ground masala for authentic flavor

This video is not just about cooking; it celebrates culture, community, and the joy of sharing delicious food. Stay until the end for a delightful tasting session that will leave you craving this wholesome delicacy!

snippet.title: मूली भरे मसाला परांठे एसे बनायें-फूले फूले-खस्ता,बेलने में न कटें न फटें- Easy-to-Roll Mooli Paratha
snippet.description:
Soft and Fluffy Mooli Stuffed Masala Paratha, Never Roll a Cracked Paratha Again, खाने में लाजवाब मूली मसाला पराठा, बेलने में आसान अब कभी भी पराठा फटेगा नहीं, बिना फटे, बिना मेहनत – मूली मसाला पराठा एसे बनायें, 
#breakfast #paratha #nashta 

Ingredients for Mooli Paratha
मूली - Radish - 2 no (500 grams)
गेहूं का आटा - Wheat flour - 2 cup (300 grams)
अजवाइन - Carom seeds - 1/2 tsp
नमक - Salt - 1/2  tsp
तेल - Oil - 1 tsp

For Stuffing
हल्दी पाउडर - Turmeric powder - 1/4 tsp
धनिया पाउडर - Coriander powder - 1/2 tsp
गरम मसाला - Garam masala - 1/4 tsp
कश्मीरी लाल मिर्च - Kashmiri red chilli - 1/2 tsp
अमचूर पाउडर - Dry mango powder - 1/2 tsp
नमक - Salt - 1/2  tsp
अदरक मिर्च पेस्ट - Ginger chilli paste - 1/2 tsp
हरा धनिया - Coriander - 2-3 tbsp

fr.title: Medical Dreams - Official Trailer | Sharman Joshi | Girliyapa Original Series | E01 out on 4th Feb
fr.description:
Four dreamers, one epic journey, and Sinha Sir’s rock-solid guidance. 🩺✨
Sapne bade hain, par raste aur bhi mushkil. Kya yeh char apni manzil tak pahuch payenge?
Watch Medical Dreams E01 on 4th Feb and find out! 🚀

#MedicalDreams #NEET2025 #Girliyapa #GirliyapaOriginalSeries 

ALLEN is where champions are created! 30+ lakh students mentored, 36+ years of excellence, and unbeatable results in NEET & JEE. Join now! https://alleninfo.in/allenpresentsmedicaldreams

Credits - 
Created by: Arunabh Kumar, Anant Singh 'Bhaatu'
Directed by: Ashutosh Pankaj 
Produced by: Arunabh Kumar
Written by: Swasti Jain, Abhishek Srivastava, Swarnadeep Biswas, Nikita Okhade
Executive Producers: Vijay Koshy, Anant Singh 'Bhaatu'
Trailer Edited By: Ajay Padwal

Cast: Sharman Joshi, Rrama Sharma, Aishwarya, Rishabh Joshi, Saloni Daini, Boloram Das, Garima Vikrant Singh, Jaya Ojha

---
This channel is owned, operated, and managed by, Contagious Online Media Network Private Limited.

Medical school aspirants know the grind like no one else. From **NEET prep** to the **MBBS dream**, the journey is anything but easy. It starts with endless hours of **study grind**, flipping through **NCERT Bible** pages, and juggling between **mock test anxiety** and **last-minute revision**. The **topper mindset** isn’t just about getting high scores; it’s about surviving the **coaching life**, decoding **mnemonics & shortcuts**, and finding ways to stay motivated despite the sleepless nights. Every medical aspirant has promised themselves **"Kal se serious"** at least once, only to be distracted by **procrastination**, the eternal enemy of every student. But when the dream is to wear that **white coat** and hold a **stethoscope**, there’s no room for giving up.  

The real adventure begins when you step into **medical college**, where the excitement of the **first dissection** is mixed with the terror of **viva** exams. Walking into the **anatomy lab struggles** feels like entering an unknown world, and **cadaver room stories** are enough to haunt even the bravest students. Then comes the **8 AM lectures**, where half the class is either sleeping or relying on **coffee-fueled nights** to stay awake. But nothing prepares you for the **36-hour shifts** of clinical rotations, where exhaustion meets **ward duty blues**, and the real learning begins. **Sleep vs. study dilemma** becomes an everyday battle, and some days, **mental breakdowns before exams** feel inevitable.  

Yet, amidst all the chaos, **study group saviors** make the journey bearable. There’s always that one friend who calls during **exam panic mode**, asking **"Bhai tune kya padha?"**, as if cramming last minute will change fate. **Late-night library sessions** turn into deep discussions about life, and **seniors vs. juniors bonding** happens over shared struggles and survival tips. Even the **professors’ legendary one-liners** become inside jokes among students. And despite the stress, **college fests & stress relief** moments remind every medical student why they chose this path in the first place.  

But medical school isn’t just about books and tests—it’s also about expectations. **Parents’ expectations** loom large, with the constant reminder of **"Doctor ban jao, phir aish hi aish"**, while reality proves otherwise. The fear of **imposter syndrome** creeps in, making students question if they truly belong here. Some dream of the day they’ll finally attend **convocation day**, while others are just trying to get through the next **clinical rotation** without passing out from exhaustion. The road to becoming a doctor is paved with challenges, but the **determination to achieve it** keeps every medical aspirant going.  

Because at the end of the day, it’s not just about **cracking NEET** or surviving **medical textbooks overload**—it’s about the passion to heal, the courage to face setbacks, and the resilience to keep going. Whether it’s the struggle of remembering every tiny detail from **pharmacology** or the joy of finally making sense of **pathology**, every step in this journey shapes the future **doctors of tomorrow**. So to every **medical school aspirant** out there, battling through **NCERT Bible**, surviving **mock test anxiety**, and chasing that **MBBS dream**—you’re not alone. The struggle is real, but so is the reward. Keep going! 💪🚀

snippet.title: కేంద్ర బడ్జెట్‌: భారీగా తగ్గనున్న ఆదాయపు పన్ను || Massive Income Tax relief in Union Budget ||
snippet.description:
#profknageshwar 
#ProfkNageshwaranalysis
#mlcnageshwar 
#budget2025 
#sitharaman 
#budget2025 
#middleclass 
#corporate 
#incometax 
#taxrelief 
 
కేంద్ర బడ్జెట్‌: భారీగా తగ్గనున్న ఆదాయపు పన్ను || Massive Income Tax relief in Union Budget ||

New income tax slabs in Budget 2025: 30% tax now starts at Rs 24 lakh, 25% tax rate introduced for incomes between Rs 20-Rs 24 lakh
Apart from rejigging the income tax slabs, the government has increased the tax rebate available under Section 87A. Due to this, an individual having net taxable income up to Rs 12 lakh will not be required to pay any tax.

The new income tax laws will be effective from the new FY 2025-26, starting from April 1, 2025, provided the proposals are passed by Parliament as presented.
https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/wealth/tax/income-tax-slab-changes-in-budget-2025/articleshow/117736311.cms?from=mdr

Episode 4307: Venu Kutti's Arrival
--------------------------------------------------------
Jethalal hatches an elaborate plan to welcome Venu Kutti. He borrows Sodhi’s car, to keep him distracted. Will his plan work out? 

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - Ep 4307 | 29 Jan 2025
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2024 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #16yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Pathikichu - Racing Version | Ajith Kumar | Anirudh Ravichander
snippet.description:
#AjithKumar #Dubai24H #RacingVictory #AjithKumarRacing #Pathikichu #vidaamuyarchi #MotivationalMusic #NeverGiveUp #Perseverance #sonymusicsouth 

In this thrilling video, witness the incredible victory of actor Ajith Kumar at the prestigious Dubai 24H Racing event, where he and his team, Ajith Kumar Racing, delivered a performance for the ages. Driven by sheer determination and unmatched passion, Ajith’s triumph is a testament to his never-ending perseverance both on and off the track.

This victory is set to the backdrop of Ajith’s upcoming film Vidamuyarchi, with the motivational track Pathikichu fueling the energy and inspiring everyone who believes in pushing through all obstacles. The song perfectly complements his relentless spirit, making this achievement even more special.

Watch as Ajith’s journey unfolds, from the intense competition on the racetrack to the emotional victory lap, showing that success is the result of hard work, dedication, and never giving up.

#AjithKumar #Dubai24H #RacingVictory #AjithKumarRacing #Pathikichu #vidaamuyarchi #MotivationalMusic #NeverGiveUp #Perseverance #SonyMusicSouth

King is kicking off 2025 with his blockbuster single ‘Stay’, which sees him jump back into his crooner mode to deliver a soaring pop anthem as he intertwines love, regret, and longing themes. Studded with a euphoric hook and a driving rhythm that keeps the energy at peak levels throughout, the song is poised to make you ‘Stay’ for a while.

snippet.title: Pre-booked Breakfast On Air India Express!! ✈️🍽️
snippet.description:
Pre-booked a ₹650 breakfast on my Air India Express flight from Bengaluru to Delhi—was it worth it? First, a little heartbreak—where’s the iconic artificial waterfall at T2? Anyway, after boarding the new Boeing 737, I found myself in a middle seat with no window (tough life). Took off with a limited outside view and soon, food arrived! T

he masala tea? Too watered down. The cheese omelette? A bit eggy at first but got better. The hara bhara kebab? Surprisingly soft and moist. The baked beans? Classic, soft, and mushy. 

But the real winner? The banana chocolate cake—dense, balanced, and a big thumbs up! Wrapped it all up with some water before dozing off, only to wake up to great weather in Delhi. Another flight, another meal reviewed—subscribe for more food and travel adventures! 

#AirIndiaExpress #FlightFood #InflightMeals #TravelDiaries #FoodReview #AviationLovers #OmeletteLove #MasalaTea #MiddleSeatStruggles #PlaneFoodie #DelhiDiaries #BangaloreAirport #SkyHigh #FoodAdventure #DCTEats
